            We're (hopefully) on the incline and Southampton are (possibly) on the decline so I'm looking for us to win this match convincingly. 2 or 3-0, 61% possession etc. This is the type of team Wenger likes playing against because they play football the "right" way, aren't aggressive and are pretty open.
